  "translations": {
    "en": "The Sheikh, the jurist Abu Ja'far narrated to us, he said: Muhammad ibn Ahmad al-Sinani narrated to us, he said: Muhammad ibn Abi Abdillah al-Kufi narrated to us, from Musa ibn Imran al-Nakha'i, from his uncle al-Husayn ibn Yazid al-Nawfali, from Ali ibn Salim, from his father, from Thabit ibn Dinar, who said:",
    "ur": "ہم سے شیخ فقیہ ابو جعفر نے بیان کیا، ثابت بن دینار سے، انہوں نے کہا:",
    "tr": "Bize Şeyh Ebu Cafer rivayet etti, Sabit b. Dinar'dan, dedi ki:",
    "fa": "شیخ فقیه ابوجعفر برای ما روایت کرد، از ثابت بن دینار، گفت:",
    "id": "Syaikh Abu Ja'far menceritakan kepada kami, dari Tsabit bin Dinar, dia berkata:",
    "bn": "শায়খ আবু জাফর আমাদের বর্ণনা করেছেন, সাবিত ইবনে দীনার থেকে, তিনি বললেন:",
    "es": "El Sheij Abu Ja'far nos narró, de Zabit ibn Dinar, quien dijo:",
    "fr": "Le Cheikh Abu Ja'far nous a rapporté, de Thabit ibn Dinar, qui a dit :",
    "de": "Der Scheich Abu Ja'far erzählte uns, von Thabit ibn Dinar, der sagte:",
    "ru": "Шейх Абу Джафар рассказал нам, от Сабита ибн Динара, который сказал:",
    "zh": "谢赫阿布·贾法尔告诉我们，从萨比特·本·迪纳尔，他说："
  }
}